dct_description_sm: "Modified Clarke 1 880 (S.A.) spheroid projection." Ancillary map: "Guide to units." Map shows three classes of roads, path tracks, fuel stations, post offices, and other relevant buildings. "Copyright reserved by the Government of Zimbabwe".
